commit.message:
Makefile.in: Rebuilt.

	* Makefile.in: Rebuilt.
	* Makefile.am (lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LDFLAGS): Link against
	libstdc++.

From-SVN: r62291

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+2003-02-02  Tom Tromey  <tromey@redhat.com>
+
+	* Makefile.in: Rebuilt.
+	* Makefile.am (lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LDFLAGS): Link against
+	libstdc++.
+
 2003-01-31  Mark WIelaard  <mark@klomp.org>
 
 	* Makefile.in: Rebuilt.

@@ -308,7 +308,8 @@ lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_SOURCES = $(x_nat_source_files)
 EXTRA_lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_SOURCES = $(x_java_source_files)
 lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_DEPENDENCIES = libgcj-@gcc_version@.jar $(x_javao_files)
 lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LIBADD = $(x_javao_files)
-lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LDFLAGS = @X_PRE_LIBS@ @X_LIBS@ -lX11 @X_EXTRA_LIBS@ \
+lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LDFLAGS = ../libstdc++-v3/src/libstdc++.la \
+	@X_PRE_LIBS@ @X_LIBS@ -lX11 @X_EXTRA_LIBS@ \
         -rpath $(toolexeclibdir) \
 ## The mysterious backslash is consumed by make.
         -version-info `grep -v '^\#' $(srcdir)/libtool-version`

@@ -390,7 +390,8 @@ lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_SOURCES = $(x_nat_source_files)
 EXTRA_lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_SOURCES = $(x_java_source_files)
 lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_DEPENDENCIES = libgcj-@gcc_version@.jar $(x_javao_files)
 lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LIBADD = $(x_javao_files)
-lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LDFLAGS = @X_PRE_LIBS@ @X_LIBS@ -lX11 @X_EXTRA_LIBS@ \
+lib_gnu_awt_xlib_la_LDFLAGS = ../libstdc++-v3/src/libstdc++.la \
+	@X_PRE_LIBS@ @X_LIBS@ -lX11 @X_EXTRA_LIBS@ \
         -rpath $(toolexeclibdir) \
         -version-info `grep -v '^\#' $(srcdir)/libtool-version`
 
@@ -2529,7 +2530,7 @@ libgcj-test.spec.in libgcj.spec.in
 
 DISTFILES = $(DIST_COMMON) $(SOURCES) $(HEADERS) $(TEXINFOS) $(EXTRA_DIST)
 
-TAR = tar
+TAR = gtar
 GZIP_ENV = --best
 DIST_SUBDIRS =  @DIRLTDL@ testsuite gcj include @DIRLTDL@ gcj include
 DEP_FILES =  .deps/$(srcdir)/$(CONVERT_DIR)/gen-from-JIS.P \
